import React from 'react'
import { Route,Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import HomePage from './Pages/HomePage'
const App = () => {
  return (
    <Routes>
       <Route path='/' element = {<HomePage />}/>
       <Route path='/login' element = {<HomePage />}/>
       <Route path='/verifyEmail' element = {<HomePage />}/>
       <Route path='/' element = {<HomePage />}/>
    </Routes>
  )
}

export default App
